Overview
At MPC Node Stats, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information when you use our application. We are committed to protecting your personal information, and we want you to know that
we do not collect any data whatsoever
â€”not even usage statistics.
Data Collection
MPC Node Stats does not collect, store, or transmit any personal or non-personal data.
This includes, but is not limited to, information such as:
Personal details (e.g., name, email, phone number)
Usage statistics or behavioral data
Location information
Any other identifiable data
Our application operates entirely without collecting any form of user data. There are no cookies, tracking mechanisms, or analytics embedded in the app.
Third-Party Services
MPC Node Stats does not integrate with any third-party services or SDKs that collect or analyze user data. All functionalities are designed to run without transmitting any information outside your device.
Data Security
Since no personal or usage data is collected or stored, there are no data storage or transfer processes that could expose your information. We do, however, maintain standard security practices to ensure the integrity of the app.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about our practices.
